    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Goibibo Advisory Limited. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Digital Marketing Manager to strengthen our Ghaziabad-based team.\n\nAbout Goibibo Advisory Limited:\nGoibibo Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Learning & development budget\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Goibibo Advisory Limited!",
